  * By default, this resource can take over management of existing users (controlled by <span pulumi-lang-nodejs="`allowExisting`" pulumi-lang-dotnet="`AllowExisting`" pulumi-lang-go="`allowExisting`" pulumi-lang-python="`allow_existing`" pulumi-lang-yaml="`allowExisting`" pulumi-lang-java="`allowExisting`">`allow_existing`</span>)
